# Package.json Scripts

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "format": "biome format --write .",
    "lint": "biome lint .",
    "check": "biome check --write .",
    "format:check": "biome format --write . --files-ignore-unknown=false",
    "lint:check": "biome lint . --files-ignore-unknown=false"
  }
}